TEM and XPS spectra were used to characterize the MnO2 NS prepared using a redox reaction between SDS and KMnO4. TEM image confirmed our successful synthesis of MnO2 NS. As shown in Fig. 2
                        a, the TEM image revealed that the MnO2 NS displayed a thin and irregular two-dimensional sheet-like structure, containing fine wrinkles which provide sufficient surface coverage for the fixation of BPEI-CDs. (See Fig. 3
                        ).
